{"tid":1887702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"阻武漢肺炎 北韓要求中國勿遣返脫北者","createTime":"2020-02-19T17:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:33:03.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5598efe54efc8e30a0e845e1ffafc6b18584fefe","tid":1887702,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4327595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4327595&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5Fm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=29ae309b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4327595</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞網站「每日北韓」記者姜美真（音譯）證實，北韓至少在上月30日就關閉邊境，「北韓人民軍下令所有檢查哨嚴加戒備，阻止任何走私行為。不管是人或貨物，都進不來也出不去」。<br />\n<br />\n路透報導，從事難民救援的一名南韓牧師說，平壤當局還要求北京勿遣返關押在中國大陸的脫北者。在中國餐廳工作的北韓民眾，也收到國家命令，要求留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n在這波武漢肺炎疫情中，北韓的公衛措施算是相當快速且有決斷力。不過哈佛大學醫學院講師、韓美醫學會北韓專案主任朴基（音譯）指出，國際制裁恐使北韓難取得醫療補給品。他說：「北韓的行動讓他們損失不少觀光及貿易收入，加上隔離外國人的花費，反映出他們對自家醫療系統是否有能力應付疫情爆發的擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n目前北韓的防堵措施仍算成功，卻也付出不小代價。姜美真說：「這不只對北韓的市場經濟有巨大影響，更嚴重的是國家整體經濟。北韓提倡在地化，但不論是糖果、餅乾或服飾，就算是國內工廠製造，原料還是來自中國大陸」。"},{"pid":"c3852b4e34ffa8c716744499de0f9b443cc05ca2","tid":1887702,"uid":294614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推下啊唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab6bf6d0fd6151fc5ae250c9b52ee758bc0c6e8","tid":1887702,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ae56c7b7c4b503d788f9ec0cd2915df8e76ff6","tid":1887702,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"金仔:咪撚俾屎我執<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e9a47c776b70dc464ec71724f0fc803959bc71","tid":1887702,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"不管是人或貨物，都進不來也出不去<br />\n<br />\n南韓魚要失業了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25da008fa4026d78e169b0f61e240df87d4d1d3f","tid":1887702,"uid":30145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"金司令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ee041961820949a857eed07cd5e77a9050aac9","tid":1887702,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:33:03.000Z","msg":"Then China will just kill NK defectors! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}